(158, '3 Small Artificial Plants in White Hexagon Pot with Bamboo Tray', 'Accessories', 'About this item\r\nPack of 3 Small, very realistic looking artificial plants in a white hexagon ceramic pot with bamboo tray - cute Home or RV greenery without having to cope with dirt and water!\r\n\r\nContact me if you would like to special order a large quantity or if you would like to add a personalized gift message to somebody!\r\n\r\nDimension of pots: 2.8’’ x 2.8’’ x 1.9’’\r\nDimension of pots including plant: 2.8\" x 2.8\" x height varies between 4.5\" and 7.0\"\r\n', '3 Small Artificial Plants in White Hexagon Pot with Bamboo Tray.WEBP', '4500.00'),
(159, 'Artificial Lavender Plant in Handmade Concrete Pot - Faux Lavender ', 'Accessories', 'About this item\r\nSmall, very realistic looking artificial lavender plant in handmade concrete Pot!\r\n\r\nPot is available in grey, white or black - Please choose color at checkout!\r\nSize including plant = 3.5\" L x 3.5\" W x 6.75\" H', 'Artificial Lavender Plant in Handmade Concrete Pot - Faux Lavender.WEBP', '3800.00'),
(160, 'Succulent Potted Plant Decoration', 'Accessories', 'About this item\r\nArtificial Flower Fake Plants Bookshelf Decor, Romantic Succulent Potted Plant \r\n\r\nMeasurement\r\nThis is small,the flower pot size is 6*5cm, the average height of the plants is about 8cm\r\n\r\nMaterial\r\nThe Succulent plant is made of PVC.\r\nThe flower pot is made of Ceramic flowerpot.\r\n\r\nPrice:\r\nThe price is for 1 plant with flower pot\r\n', 'Succulent Potted Plant Decoration.WEBP', '450.00'),
(161, 'Handmade ceramics tealight candle holder bookshelf decor', 'Accessories', 'About this item\r\nThis is complete imitation of the old Riga house. The ceramic house is made of clay. The house is used as a candlestick. The light of the candle inside the house illuminates the miniature windows and creates a feeling of warmth and coziness. This house can be wonderful and heartwarming gift for an adult and a child for any holiday or special occasion.\r\n\r\nHouse height about 15 cm (5.9 inch), width 9 cm (3.54 inch), depth 7.5 cm (2.95 inch).\r\n', 'Handmade ceramics tealight candle holder bookshelf decor.WEBP', '1300.00'),
(162, 'Books Candle', 'Accessories', 'It is made from high-quality soy wax, which ensures a clean and long-lasting burn. The candle is unscented, allowing you to enjoy the natural scent of the soy wax without any added fragrance.\r\n\r\nThe Books Candle is not only a functional item but also a beautiful decorative piece. Its elegant and minimalist design makes it a perfect addition to any space, whether it\'s your living room, bedroom, or office. ', 'Books Candle.WEBP', '700.00'),
(163, 'Small Bronze Paper boat Sculpture', 'Accessories', 'Dimensions:\r\n\r\nHeight : 3cm / 1.1 inches\r\nWidth : 4cm / 1.5 inches\r\nDepth : 7.5cm / 2.9 inches\r\n\r\nWeight : 50gr', 'Small Bronze Paperboat Sculpture.WEBP', '850.00'),
(164, 'Grim Reaper Sitting Bookshelf Decor', 'Accessories', 'About this item\r\nThis ghostly grim reaper figurine is perfect for all your gothic novels! Death comes with a teacup (*not attached) that you can place on his lap, next to him on the shelf, where ever you wish.\r\n\r\nMeasurements -\r\nSmall - 3.5 inches tall total, 2.5 inches above the waist.\r\nMedium - 5 inches tall total, 4 inches above the waist', 'Grim Reaper Sitting Bookshelf Decor.WEBP', '350.00'),
