(372, '41 ISLAMIC MORAL STORIES FOR CHILDREN', 'Education and Textbooks', 'Key Benefits:\r\n41 Islamic Moral Stories for Children is a compilation of a variety of interesting stories that provide sound advice and valuable examples. Each character in every story imparts the religious mannerisms (behaviors) that can be easily understood and copied by young children because the stories are taught in the way that our religion has always been taught.\r\nEnlightening Tales for Young Minds\r\nImmerse Your Child in Moral Education with “41 Islamic Moral Stories for Children.”\r\nUnlock the gateway to enriching your child’s moral compass with a collection of captivating tales rooted in Islamic teachings. Each story serves as a beacon of wisdom, guiding young hearts towards valuable life lessons.\r\n\r\n1. Nurturing Faith and Virtue\r\nTake your child on a spiritual journey with tales that embody faith and virtue. These stories, rich with empathy and righteousness, instill Islamic values and nurture a sense of purpose in young minds.\r\n\r\n2. Cultivating Moral Integrity\r\nElevate your child’s understanding of moral integrity through narratives that illuminate the path of righteousness. Each story teaches kindness and honesty, guiding children to develop a strong moral compass and make ethical decisions confidently.\r\n\r\n3. Inspiring Empathy and Compassion\r\nImmerse your child in narratives that resonate with the beauty of empathy and compassion. Through heartfelt stories of empathy and compassion, children learn the profound impact of kindness and empathy, fostering a sense of interconnectedness with the world around them', '41 ISLAMIC MORAL STORIES FOR CHILDREN.WEBP', '1095.00'),
(374, 'Wren & Martin’s Primary School English Grammar & Composition', 'Education and Textbooks', 'Wren & Martin’s Primary School English Grammar & Composition is a grammar textbook designed to be used as a prequel to the highly popular English grammar reference book, High School English Grammar & Composition. This book provides ample guidance and practice in sentence building, correct usage, comprehension, composition, and other related areas to equip the learners with the ability to communicate effectively in English.', 'PARAMOUNT PRIMARY SCHOOL ENGLISH GRAMMAR AND COMPOSITION MULTICOLOUR EDITION.WEBP', '995.00');
